Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BotResponse
    For storing bot responses, mainly to allow a short pause on a separate thread to improve the interactivity of the machine.
    ButtonListener
    The class which listens for buttons to be pressed.
    Conversation
    A class which enables Conversation objects, which hold the successive responses generated during the course of a conversation with a bot or yourself.
    FileMenuListener
    The class that listens to the inputs from the File menu of the GUI, and knows what to do for each menu element.
    InputListener
    The class that handles input fromt input frame in the main GUI
    Main
    The Main class of the WebAgent, where everything starts and everything comes together.
    Response
    An object which holds response content plus a vector of responses which have been next in the past, which expands if new responses occur
    ResponseList
    The one-dimensional list of responses ever entered, each index corresponds to the ID that the Response is assigned.
    ResponseMatrix
    The representation of the memory graph as an adjacency matrix
    WebAgentDB
    A class which has methods and variables to do with the connection to the mySQL server by which WebAgent backs up and can retrieve and analyze data.
    WebAgentUI
    A class which mainly puts together and instantiates GUI elements for the main GUI interface.
